option.value:
from django.db import models
# Create your models here.
class Plan(models.Model): rango = models.ForeignKey(Rango, on_delete=models.CASCADE) tipo = models.CharField(max_length=50) recomendaciones = models.TextField()
def __str__(self): return f"{self.tipo} - {self.rango}"
